item.title: CVE-2020-2132|2024-08-04T07:01:40.632Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20parasoft%20environment%20manager%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Parasoft Environment Manager Plugin 2.14 and earlier stores a password unencrypted in job config.xml files on the Jenkins master where it can be viewed by users with Extended Read permission, or access to the master file system.
